message.content:
cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the problem of single-view depth prediction, which is a fundamental problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes to use deep learning methods to solve the problem and presents a large depth dataset called MegaDepth. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses modern structure-from-motion and multi-view stereo (MVS) methods to generate training data from multi-view Internet photo collections. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating 3D reconstructions from 2D images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with using large amounts of Internet data to generate training data for single-view depth prediction.
